&lt;p&gt;Applicants are invited for the post of General Paediatric Clinical Fellow at Whittington Hospital. The successful applicants will join a strong clinical team, participate in the general paediatric SHO rota and have the same educational opportunities as doctors in formal training posts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For an informal discussion via email please contact Dr Sunita Rao (sunita.rao@nhs.net)&lt;/p&gt;
